  "texts": [
    "It would make sense to first seek outpatient psychosomatic treatment to help the patient cope with her pain and focus on long-term recovery.In this example, it is evident that GPT-4 knows the facts (remember), understands them (understand), applies them to this situation (apply), and correctly analyzes the situation (analyze).",
    "GPT-4 can even be observed to evaluate, but it fails at evaluating the consequences of its decision.",
    "While GPT-4 seems to be aware of this and wants to modify the given answer, it incorrectly evaluates the answer options and does not recommend inpatient psychosomatic treatment.",
    "Discussion Principal FindingsTools based on LLMs are rapidly evolving and influencing medicine [1] and medical education [2].",
